<plot>In the canyons of northern New Mexico, a mystical stranger on horse back confronts Elias, a twelve-year-old boy. The stranger gives Elias a mission to face his fears and stand against a growing darkness, a mission to show that the age of miracles still exists. Elias chooses to stand against ridicule and risk his life to stand for what he knows is true. Elias faith restores hope at a time when a small town is being pulled apart by the trial of a local teenager.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?175338</url></doc>
